                     <interp inst="t18220911-17-person170" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and live at Aldgate. I found the prisoner at the Bull's Head, public-house, charged with this. He said he had stolen them, and was sorry for it - that he had left his own clothes at a public-house.</p>
